Please summarize the following email chain:

Email: Subject: Project Update
Dear Team, The project is moving ahead as planned. We're currently in the design phase and expect to start development next week. Regards, Alice

Email: Subject: RE: Project Update
Hi Alice, That's great news! Please make sure to update the project timeline accordingly. Best, Bob

Email: Subject: RE: RE: Project Update
Will do, Bob. I'll send the updated timeline by end of day. Cheers, Alice

The email chain discusses the progress of a project currently in the design phase, with development expected to start the following week. Bob asked Alice to update the project timeline accordingly, to which Alice agreed to send the updated timeline by the end of the day.
